        "rendered": "<p>Go back to the list of Blocks The Group block allows you to group different blocks together and customize them to your liking, including setting custom background colors, spacing, and more. Adding a Group block To add a Group block, click on the Block Inserter icon. You can also type /group and hit enter in [&hellip;]</p>\n",
